  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[nodebrewでnode.jsをインストール]]></title>
    <link href="http://kawahiro311.github.io/blog/2013/11/29/install-node-dot-js-by-nodebrew/"/>
    <updated>2013-11-29T16:39:07+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://kawahiro311.github.io/blog/2013/11/29/install-node-dot-js-by-nodebrew</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>node.jsのバージョン管理システム<br/>
<a href="https://github.com/hokaccha/nodebrew">https://github.com/hokaccha/nodebrew</a></p>

<h4>インストール(github 公式documentより)</h4>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ curl -L git.io/nodebrew | perl - setup
</span><span class='line'>...
</span><span class='line'>install nodebrew in $HOME/.nodebrew
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>========================================
</span><span class='line'>Add path:
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>export PATH=$HOME/.nodebrew/current/bin:$PATH
</span><span class='line'>========================================</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>~/.zshrcに追加</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>export PATH=$HOME/.nodebrew/current/bin:$PATH</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ source ~/.zshrc
</span><span class='line'>$ nodebrew help</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><a href="http://nodejs.org/">http://nodejs.org/</a> とかから最新のversion調べて、インストール</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ nodebrew install v0.10.22</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>確認、インストールしたものを使用</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ nodebrew ls
</span><span class='line'>$ nodebrew use v0.10.22
</span><span class='line'>$ node -v
</span><span class='line'>v0.10.22</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>参考</h4>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://qiita.com/sinmetal/items/154e81823f386279b33c">http://qiita.com/sinmetal/items/154e81823f386279b33c</a></li>
<li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/11177954/how-do-i-completely-uninstall-node-js-and-reinstall-from-beginning-mac-os-x">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/11177954/how-do-i-completely-uninstall-node-js-and-reinstall-from-beginning-mac-os-x</a> (nodebrew以外でインストールした場合のuninstall方法)</li>
</ul>

]]></content>
